<L>__{interior hitchcock house, kitchen night}
<A>__{a fridge door snaps open to reveal hitchcock's face in the darkness. he's in his pajamas. his hand trembles next to a stack of chicken breasts and moves to an upturned grapefruit half at the back of the shelf. he pulls it out it to reveal a hidden stash of foie gras under the hollowed out grapefruit. he's about to devour it when he catches sight of his distorted reflection in the chrome shelving. he backs away, disgusted at this monster before him, the light of the fridge illuminating his expression.}
